Open *.po files in Poedit (>=1.5.4):
  http://www.poedit.net

Poedit Configutration:

* Add  *.php and *.phtml to your parser:
  [PoEdit] > Preferences > Parsers --> PHP > [Edit]

  - List of extensions...:
    *.php;*.phtml

  - Parser command:
    xgettext --force-po -o %o %C %K %F --language=PHP
